c-Du/Th%C6%B0-th%C3%A1n/poem-6E7FIE6gDHSy2UWGhlL-Jg">Thư thán - 書嘆</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%E1%BB%A5c-Du/author-6xOAUbKdWiBr-eAAn9zXQQ">Lục Du</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Ngh%E1%BB%87/Ti%E1%BB%85n-%C4%90%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-V%C4%A9nh-X%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/poem-REFcxsHN0Qkbnz8_E0SczQ">Tiễn Đường Vĩnh Xương - 餞唐永昌</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Ngh%E1%BB%87/author-QDWzzxQ3HcTaWqr27wbrqQ">Lý Nghệ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90o%C3%A0n-Huy%C3%AAn/Ti%E1%BB%85n-Gia-L%C3%A2m-hu%E1%BA%A5n-%C4%91%E1%BA%A1o-Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Do%C3%A3n-V%E1%BB%8Dng-th%C4%83ng-B%C3%ACnh-S%C6%A1n-tri-huy%E1%BB%87n/poem-dLVE5-TRW-rvnoQ9L9OqLg">Tiễn Gia Lâm huấn đạo Nguyễn Doãn Vọng thăng Bình Sơn tri huyện - 餞嘉林訓導阮允望升平山知縣</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90o%C3%A0n-Huy%C3%AAn/author-h3EvqeQvlQUxq2sceUWWYQ">Đoàn Huyên</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Y%E1%BA%BFt-H%E1%BB%81-T%C6%B0/V%C5%A9-thu%E1%BA%ADt-tam-thi%C3%AAn-k%E1%BB%B3-3/poem-T6z1-FRywBFCAaxAOBr3bg">Vũ thuật tam thiên kỳ 3 - 雨述三篇其三</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Y%E1%BA%BFt-H%E1%BB%81-T%C6%B0/author-iORDIpdUm3k9JfYMnUFi-Q">Yết Hề Tư</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
